---
import { Users, Shield, Zap } from "lucide-astro";
---

<section class="py-20 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
        Why Choose Open Source?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Discover the benefits of open source software and why millions choose it
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <Users class="h-8 w-8 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
          Community Driven
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
          Built by passionate developers worldwide, open source software benefits from diverse perspectives and continuous improvement.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <Shield class="h-8 w-8 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
          Transparent & Secure
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
          Source code is publicly available, allowing for security audits and ensuring no hidden backdoors or malicious code.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <Zap class="h-8 w-8 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
          Cost Effective
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
          Most open source software is free to use, helping businesses and individuals save on licensing costs while getting enterprise-grade features.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
